{
  "stem": "11998.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I don't think that they were a tool of the divine will.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I feel that they were pursuing their own interests.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And that's basically what it was.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They, they needed, they needed a scapegoat.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They had a ready-made enemy among them from which they could organize themselves around and fight a very, very effective fight.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I think the prejudice was there, which was there for 2,000 years through the Christian teachings.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And the climate was ripe.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Jews in Germany had attained a certain amount of establishment [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] status.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "They became wealthy.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And they lived a good life.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And it was, in the eyes of a lot of Germans who did not have jobs, who were very poor, and especially in the 1930s, where a runaway inflation, and Jews lived a good life.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And there was a guy that came and started agitating that it is the Jews' fault that, that is destroying Germany.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "So it was-- But my own belief came back after the war when I started studying Judaism from a more serious point of view or more adult or-- point of view.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And I came to the conclusion that [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] also God was silent.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "I don't think he was dead.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You mean during the, during the, During the war?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, it started in 1938 and '39, as I indicated before, that we had an overflow of anti-Semitism.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "After the death of Pilsudski, who was the president of Poland, other people took office.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they became much more anti-Semitic in their, in their attitude toward the Jewish people, yeah.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I think he died in 1938.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And so it turned, it turned very rapidly and very ugly.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
